<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
Nesh Ohr has something to ask you.
Lie in wait at the designated location and defeat the father of armored dragons.
Come closer, little one. I must ask thee─did a pitiable dragonet meet its end at thy hand?
Though I cannot find it in my heart to thank thee, nor shall I admonish thee. The young one would have suffered every living moment...as do we all, though some torments are more easily borne.
If thou wouldst prevent further needless suffering, pray seek my shelled kin at the shallow lake. He hath wallowed overlong in hatred beyond healing.
Wait by the waterside, and he will find thee.
...So it is done. I heard his dying cry.
His bloodline was the strongest of the armored ones, possessed of carapaces like unto stone. Yet even they were not impervious to the metal fiends' onslaught.
It took but one to raze their nest. Even now, its terrible form doth linger in my mind─the four jaws that ravened 'neath a shroud of steel...
And to the few who escaped the carnage, life has gifted naught but despair. They yearn for vengeance, though our enemy has long since quit this place.
As thou hast witnessed, they now turn all too quickly to indiscriminate violence... Alas, this only feedeth the fires of their guilt─never doth it quell them.
Nay, I fear that only death hath that power.
